{"tid":353970,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Excel高手有冇人幫下我","createTime":"2017-08-10T04:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T15:18:31.000Z","uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2eaa6abcfa73425e52a24a452deed551899e5f81","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"而家我想咁做：<br />\n<br />\n個source裡面有十幾格<br />\n<br />\n會想係大於50先count 佢一格，後面仲有有單位（文字）顯示<br />\n<br />\n但唔大過50就唔想果喥有野顯顯示<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<br />\n超市入面有<br />\n米 $80 汔水 $10 鮑魚 $200<br />\n<br />\n七仔入面有<br />\n啤酒一箱 $70  糖 $20  藥 $50<br />\n<br />\n文具店有<br />\n筆$10 擦膠 $5<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我想出嘅句子係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>超市有 2 件貨貴過$50，七仔有 2 件貨貴過$50</strong><br />\n<br />\n（因為文具店無野貴過$50，所以句子無顯示）<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講下我應該點樣寫條formula<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84302c1d44cc78764e97e767b841f0e57a949446","tid":353970,"uid":117978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count"},{"pid":"922c392e2348640ebb89374d20f8420f851cc094","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"如果想乜都出晒就當然用countif 已ok<br />\n但想佢唔出，咁係咪前面又要加if?"},{"pid":"bb23d6a75830da5e231aa8048346d93d37ceeb8a","tid":353970,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"試下用COUNTIF"},{"pid":"b47619cdbf616040243a0ace485fd7c0a9d75140","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要excel"},{"pid":"438ee18bfa6f8444afc24c7160b8e0e1f456514c","tid":353970,"uid":19979,"like":16,"dislike":1,"