&gt;$50\t2\t\t\t1\t\t\t0</span><br />\n<br />\n咁??</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n但後面要有埋字<br />\n0左嘅唔出現"},{"pid":"492b52a71d57f269e84e8a12442f6788bc36392e","tid":353970,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法"},{"pid":"a2dda3e00642396c8e025b3f60df187956b8c023","tid":353970,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"單位手打同set format 會唔同玩法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbb59584c54f1d2e629e908c56a572504a242bb","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>If 你出糧比我<br />\nThen 我會幫你做<br />\nElse 自己google<br />\nEnd if</blockquote><br />\nGoogle到唔洗問<br />\n我頭先如果所有野用count if做係做到個結果出黎會係<br />\n超市有2件，七仔有2件，文具鋪有0件<br />\n<br />\n但問題我唔想0件果句出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係咪每個位嘅countif前面再加if咁做？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640c2474aa01d3d6e5e868b22505f6d38743bb66","tid":353970,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>If 你出糧比我<br />\nThen 我會幫你做<br />\nElse 自己google<br />\nEnd if</blockquote><br />\nGoogle到唔洗問<br />\n我頭先如果所有野用count if做係做到個結果出黎會係<br />\n超市有2件，七仔有2件，文具鋪有0件<br />\n<br />\n但問題我唔想0件果句出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係咪每個位嘅countif前面再加if咁做？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIF(COUNTIF個個CELL&gt;0,&quot;文具鋪有X件&quot;,&quot;&quot;)"},{"pid":"6185340f0a011aa5029e2859d5b9bd94cb4a4b9a","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換言之我唔能夠一條formula 寫晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7841da6ca093bfbcbc1d8a5fd818adf81e5f1f9c","tid":353970,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換言之我唔能夠一條formula 寫晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<br />\n可以<br />\n我懶得寫晒出黎姐<br />\n同埋你分開寫你第時改野, 改input都易D<br />\n不過你個要求COUNTIF + IF已經可以做晒"},{"pid":"5eed6be3efa51008c8d20e5ad1d1078b0a16a957","tid":353970,"uid":114421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換言之我唔能夠一條formula 寫晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上正解<br />\n你可以試下一條formula寫哂但就算比你試到都會亂到仆街 又易出錯 何苦呢"},{"pid":"0ac5eaa47e620d25149a01a68ec3e9d4cd66e49c","tid":353970,"uid":93245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要excel</blockquote><br />\nexcel vba</blockquote><br />\n用for loop好<br />\n<br />\nfor counter1號 = 頭 to 尾<br />\n<br />\nif 數字&gt;50 then<br />\ncounter2號=counter2號+1<br />\nend if<br />\n<br />\nnext counter 2號<br />\n<br />\nRange(&quot;A1&quot;) = counter 2號<br />\n<br />\n搞掂"},{"pid":"68195b50bc49621803b665391d3bae27a435b146","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換言之我唔能夠一條formula 寫晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<br />\n可以<br />\n我懶得寫晒出黎姐<br />\n同埋你分開寫你第時改野, 改input都易D<br />\n不過你個要求COUNTIF + IF已經可以做晒</blockquote><br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfaf0c6931851dafca67d873defba7709793ceb","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>XX一個CELL<br />\nCOUNTIF 分三個CELL先<br />\n<br />\n個數會係0至3<br />\n<br />\n之後你咪用=IF(A1&gt;0,&quot;超市內有&quot;&amp;上面個CELL&amp;&quot;件貨品貴過XX)&amp;IF(A2&gt;0,&quot;7仔內有&quot;.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣寫法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換言之我唔能夠一條formula 寫晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上正解<br />\n你可以試下一條formula寫哂但就算比你試到都會亂到仆街 又易出錯 何苦呢</blockquote><br />\n明白晒<br />\n我就係因為寫太長勁打kick"},{"pid":"76574a79217a1923bb309ba07cb2341819945277","tid":353970,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要excel</blockquote><br />\nexcel vba</blockquote><br />\n用for loop好<br />\n<br />\nfor counter1號 = 頭 to 尾<br />\n<br />\nif 數字&gt;50 then<br />\ncounter2號=counter2號+1<br />\nend if<br />\n<br />\nnext counter 2號<br />\n<br />\nRange(&quot;A1&quot;) = counter 2號<br />\n<br />\n搞掂</blockquote><br />\n我唔識用vba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291bdc5478ceabbfc93f43fccafa1c444a512a41","tid":353970,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要excel</blockquote><br />\nexcel vba</blockquote><br />\n用for loop好<br />\n<br />\nfor counter1號 = 頭 to 尾<br />\n<br />\nif 數字&gt;50 then<br />\ncounter2號=counter2號+1<br />\nend if<br />\n<br />\nnext counter 2號<br />\n<br />\nRange(&quot;A1&quot;) = counter 2號<br />\n<br />\n搞掂</blockquote><br />\n我唔識用vba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁簡單用乜鬼vba<br />\n唔洗用vba既盡量唔好用<br />\n當你好似我咁公司開十幾個excel幾十個macro你就明<br />\n部機嚴重唔夠resources"},{"pid":"4a340f6599b6b076d2c6a31a0e958453060639f3","tid":353970,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"用if、countif就做到<br />\n串連成句用埋 &amp;  同 &quot;<br />\n自己諗下先啦，唔難"},{"pid":"1ffb221bbb79f2ca1b1d12341dd879ff46bcbcc9","tid":353970,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>vb,就識<br />\nforloop<br />\n  if cell &gt; 50<br />\n      ++count</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要excel</blockquote><br />\nexcel vba</blockquote><br />\n用for loop好<br />\n<br />\nfor counter1號 = 頭 to 尾<br />\n<br />\nif 數字&gt;50 then<br />\ncounter2號=counter2號+1<br />\nend if<br />\n<br />\nnext counter 2號<br />\n<br />\nRange(&quot;A1&quot;) = counter 2號<br />\n<br />\n搞掂</blockquote><br />\n我唔識用vba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁簡單用乜鬼vba<br />\n唔洗用vba既盡量唔好用<br />\n當你好似我咁公司開十幾個excel幾十個macro你就明<br />\n部機嚴重唔夠resources</blockquote><br />\n樓主個case使撚用VBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪濫用VBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}